## ShadCN Button Variants
Verwende NUR diese Button Variants aus `/ui/button.tsx`:
- `default` - Standard Button (gefüllt)
- `outline` - Button mit Rahmen
- `ghost` - Transparenter Button
- `link` - Link-Style Button
- `destructive` - Rot für Lösch-Aktionen
- `secondary` - Sekundärer Button Style

**Beispiel:**
```tsx
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'

<Button variant="default">{text}</Button>
<Button variant="outline">{text}</Button>
<Button variant="ghost">{text}</Button>
```

## Relume Repository Struktur
- Repo: Private GitHub Repository
- Base Path: `relume/`
- Ordnerstruktur:
  - `relume/Header/` - Navbars & Heroes (HeroHeader1-19)
  - `relume/Footer/` - Footer Komponenten
  - `relume/{Category}/` - Block Komponenten (Banners, Blog, CTA, FAQ, etc.)

## Naming Conventions

### Navbar
- Input: "Navbar1"
- Repo Path: `relume/Header/Navbar1.tsx`

### Footer
- Input: "Footer1"
- Repo Path: `relume/Footer/Footer1.tsx`

### Heroes (SPEZIALFALL!)
- Input: "Header1" oder "HeroHeader1"
- Repo Path: `relume/Header/HeroHeader1.tsx`
- Normalisierung: "Header1" → "HeroHeader1"

### Blocks
- Input: "CTA2", "FAQ5", "Contact1"
- Repo Path: `relume/{Category}/{BlockName}.tsx`
- Auto-detect Category aus Namen

## Ordnerstruktur PayloadCMS
```
/src/Header/ - Navbar (MobileNav.tsx, DesktopNav.tsx, config.ts)
/src/Footer/ - Footer (MobileFooter.tsx, DesktopFooter.tsx, config.ts)
/src/heroes/{HeroName}/ - Hero Sektionen (index.tsx)
/src/heroes/config.ts - Shared Hero Block Config
/src/blocks/{Category}/{BlockName}/ - Blöcke (Component.tsx, config.ts, index.ts)
```

